Todo:
1. In level 1, on clicking image of each and every season, instead of calling the default on_mouse_press event, call a method which gives information about that particular season to the kidin a pop-up rectangular box. The information about the season may include the months, fruits and vegetables and festivals etc.

2. In level 2, organize a small quiz and maintain the score. The quiz includes a 4-option question showing an image asking the kid to recognize the season. 
